foods.ingredients: STONE GROUND 100% WHOLE WHEAT, 100% WHOLE GRAINS (CRACKED WHEAT, BARLEY, CORN MILLET, OATS, FLAX, RYE, SESAME, TRITICALE, BROWN RICE, SOY), WATER, 100% CANOLA OIL, SOY FIBER, BAKING POWDER, (SODIUM BICARBONATE, CALCIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE), CALCIUM CARBONATE, SALT, FUMARIC ACID, MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, CALCIUM PROPIONATE, REFINED MENHADEN FISH OIL (SOURCE OF LONG CHAIN OMEGA-3 FATTY ACIDS EPH/DHA), XANTHAN GUM, GUAR GUM, POTASSIUM SORBATE*.
